  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/c7fc6a9f3c6e242d6ae957f247bcb708.avif?t=1762814451\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use your tongue to climb higher and higher! \"Stick Tongue\"</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humanity has destroyed the planet. No water, no resources, just ruins and despair. But Frogus, a daring frog, has an idea:<strong> climb to the sky to ask God for rain.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/f463331219c3ed61d7b96f018f4669fb.poster.avif?t=1762814451\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/f463331219c3ed61d7b96f018f4669fb.webm?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/f463331219c3ed61d7b96f018f4669fb.mp4?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Frogus' tongue as a grappling</strong> hook to climb a vertical world ravaged by humanity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-based gameplay </strong>: every tongue shot is a chance to rise or fall.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An adventure as absurd as it is epic</strong>, in a world where everything hinges on a frog.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/478486188d5946e5383e6b7718572250.poster.avif?t=1762814451\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/478486188d5946e5383e6b7718572250.webm?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/478486188d5946e5383e6b7718572250.mp4?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4 Game Modes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beginner Mode : </strong> Each flag you reach becomes an infinite reappearance point, allowing you to repeat as many times as necessary.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Normal Mode </strong>: You only have 3 reappearances per flag, and to regain flag you'll have to reach the next one.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extreme Mode :</strong> No Flag, No Reappearance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Jump Mode : </strong>You can't jump, you've only got your tongue!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/3515191691ebbd31c8d356c446b347f8.poster.avif?t=1762814451\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/3515191691ebbd31c8d356c446b347f8.webm?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/3515191691ebbd31c8d356c446b347f8.mp4?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Make the rain fall and save what's left of the Earth!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/c7fc6a9f3c6e242d6ae957f247bcb708.avif?t=1762814451\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use your tongue to climb higher and higher! \"Stick Tongue\"</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humanity has destroyed the planet. No water, no resources, just ruins and despair. But Frogus, a daring frog, has an idea:<strong> climb to the sky to ask God for rain.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/f463331219c3ed61d7b96f018f4669fb.poster.avif?t=1762814451\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/f463331219c3ed61d7b96f018f4669fb.webm?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/f463331219c3ed61d7b96f018f4669fb.mp4?t=1762814451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Frogus' tongue as a grappling</strong> hook to climb a vertical world ravaged by humanity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-based gameplay </strong>: every tongue shot is a chance to rise or fall.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An adventure as absurd as it is epic</strong>, in a world where everything hinges on a frog.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356480/extras/478486188d5946e5383e6b7718572250.poster.avif?t=1762814451\" width=480 height=3